('ONET-TREE_TRIMMERS_AND_PRUNERS', 'source_onet_tree_trimmers_and_pruners', 'Tree Trimmers and Pruners', 'Tree Trimmers and Pruners is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Using sophisticated climbing and rigging techniques, cut away dead or excess branches from trees or shrubs to maintain right-of-way for roads, sidewalks, or utilities, or to improve appearance, health, and value of tree. Prune or treat trees or shrubs using handsaws, hand pruners, clippers, and power pruners. Works off the ground in the tree canopy and may use truck-mounted lifts.', ARRAY['Arborist','Brush Clearing Laborer','Bucket Operator','Bucket Truck Operator','Climber','Climber Trimmer','Climbing Arborist','Diagnostician','Grape Pruner','Grounds Worker','Groundsman','Groundsperson','Laborer','Line Clearance Trimmer','Line Clearing Tree Trimmer','Plant Health Care Technician','Pruner','Sales Arborist','Tanbark Laborer','Timber Cutter','Tree Climber','Tree Doctor','Tree Expert','Tree Pruner','Tree Specialist','Tree Surgeon','Tree Trimmer','Tree Worker','Trimmer','Utility Arborist','Vine Pruner']::text[], ARRAY['Tree Trimmers and Pruners','Arborist','Brush Clearing Laborer','Bucket Operator','Bucket Truck Operator','Climber','Climber Trimmer','Climbing Arborist','Diagnostician','Grape Pruner','Grounds Worker','Groundsman','Groundsperson','Laborer','Line Clearance Trimmer','Line Clearing Tree Trimmer','Plant Health Care Technician','Pruner','Sales Arborist','Tanbark Laborer','Timber Cutter','Tree Climber','Tree Doctor','Tree Expert','Tree Pruner','Tree Specialist']::text[], ARRAY['Reading Comprehension','Active Listening','Writing','Speaking','Mathematics','Science','Critical Thinking','Active Learning','Learning Strategies','Monitoring','Social Perceptiveness','Coordination','Persuasion','Negotiation','Instructing','Service Orientation','Complex Problem Solving','Operations Analysis','Technology Design','Equipment