('ONET-ANIMAL_CARETAKERS', 'source_onet_animal_caretakers', 'Animal Caretakers', 'Animal Caretakers is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Feed, water, groom, bathe, exercise, or otherwise provide care to promote and maintain the well-being of pets and other animals that are not raised for consumption, such as dogs, cats, race horses, ornamental fish or birds, zoo animals, and mice. Work in settings such as kennels, animal shelters, zoos, circuses, and aquariums. May keep records of feedings, treatments, and animals received or discharged. May clean, disinfect, and repair cages, pens, or fish tanks.', ARRAY['Animal Care Attendant','Animal Care Giver (ACG)','Animal Care Service Worker','Animal Care Specialist','Animal Care Taker','Animal Care Technician','Animal Caregiver','Animal Caretaker','Animal Daycare Provider','Animal Feeder','Animal Groomer','Animal Handler','Animal Health Technician','Animal Keeper','Animal Nursery Worker','Animal Rehabilitator','Animal Shelter Worker','Animal Sitter','Aquarist','Aquarium Tank Attendant','Aviculturist','Bather','Bird Raiser','Bird Tender','Canary Raiser','Care Assistant','Care Taker','Caretaker','Cat Bather','Cat Groomer','Cat Sitter','Dog Barber','Dog Bather','Dog Beautician','Dog Boarder','Dog Daycare Attendant','Dog Groomer','Dog Hair Clipper','Dog Pound Attendant','Dog Raiser','Dog Sitter','Dog Walker','Farrier','Groomer','Horseshoer','Hot Walker','Keeper','Kennel Aide','Kennel Assistant','Kennel Attendant']::text[], ARRAY['Animal Caretakers','Animal Care Attendant','Animal Care Giver (ACG)','Animal Care Service Worker','Animal Care Specialist','Animal Care Taker','Animal Care Technician','Animal Caregiver','Animal Caretaker','Animal Daycare Provider','Animal Feeder','Animal Groomer','Animal Handler','Animal Health Technician','Animal Keeper','Animal Nursery Worker','Animal Rehabilitator','Animal Shelter Worker','Animal Sitter','Aquarist',