('ONET-CREDIT_AUTHORIZERS_CHECKERS_AND_CLERKS', 'source_onet_credit_authorizers_checkers_and_clerks', 'Credit Authorizers, Checkers, and Clerks', 'Credit Authorizers, Checkers, and Clerks is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Authorize credit charges against customers'' accounts. Investigate history and credit standing of individuals or business establishments applying for credit. May interview applicants to obtain personal and financial data, determine credit worthiness, process applications, and notify customers of acceptance or rejection of credit.', ARRAY['Accounts Receivable Coordinator','Authorizer','Branch Processor','Call Out Operator','Charge Authorizer','Collector','Commercial Credit Advisor','Commercial Credit Analyst','Commercial Credit Officer','Commercial Credit Reviewer','Commercial Loan Reviewer','Commercial Processor','Consumer Credit Analyst','Controller','Credit Adjuster','Credit Administrator','Credit Analyst','Credit and Collections Coordinator','Credit and Collections Specialist','Credit Assistant','Credit Associate','Credit Authorizer','Credit Balance Specialist','Credit Card Specialist','Credit Charge Authorizer','Credit Checker','Credit Clerk','Credit Coordinator','Credit Expert','Credit Historian','Credit Interviewer','Credit Investigator','Credit Letter Specialist','Credit Officer','Credit Operations Processor','Credit Processor','Credit Products Officer','Credit Professional','Credit Rating Checker','Credit Rating Inspector','Credit Reference Clerk','Credit Report Checker','Credit Reporter','Credit Representative','Credit Review Officer','Credit Review Specialist','Credit Reviewer','Credit Risk Officer','Credit Risk Review Officer','Credit Risk Specialist']::text[], ARRAY['Credit Authorizers, Checkers, and Clerks','Accounts Receivable Coordinator','Authorizer','Branch Processor','Call Out Operator','Charge Authorizer','Collector','Commercial Credit Advisor