('ONET-FOREST_AND_CONSERVATION_WORKERS', 'source_onet_forest_and_conservation_workers', 'Forest and Conservation Workers', 'Forest and Conservation Workers is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Under supervision, perform manual labor necessary to develop, maintain, or protect areas such as forests, forested areas, woodlands, wetlands, and rangelands through such activities as raising and transporting seedlings; combating insects, pests, and diseases harmful to plant life; and building structures to control water, erosion, and leaching of soil. Includes forester aides, seedling pullers, tree planters, and gatherers of nontimber forestry products such as pine straw.', ARRAY['Blister Rust Eradicator','Box Chipper','Box Cutter','Brusher','Chemical Sprayer','Chopper','Christmas Tree Farm Worker','Christmas Tree Farmer','Christmas Tree Grader','Christmas Tree Grower','Cone Picker','Conservation Coordinator','Conservation Officer','Conservation Specialist','Conservation Worker','Dipper','Environmental Field Laborer','Fern Cutter','Fern Gatherer','Fern Picker','Field Laborer','Forest Aide','Forest and Conservation Worker','Forest Nursery Worker','Forest Products Gatherer','Forest Ranger','Forest Resource Specialist','Forest Worker','Forester Aide','Forestry Aide','Forestry Conservation Worker','Forestry Farm Laborer','Forestry Laborer','Forestry Support Specialist','Forestry Worker','Gatherer','Greens Picker','Grounds Crewman','Growth Hacker','Gum Dipper','Hacker','Land Conservation Specialist','Land Steward','Moss Picker','Natural Resources Specialist','Nut Picker','Palm Gatherer','Park Maintainer','Pine Straw Gatherer','Pitch Gatherer']::text[], ARRAY['Forest and Conservation Workers','Blister Rust Eradicator','Box Chipper','Box Cutter','Brusher','Chemical Sprayer','Chopper','Christmas Tree Farm Worker','Christmas Tree Farmer','Christmas Tree Grader','Christmas Tree Grower','Cone Picker','